<function>

access:   public

name: setQuery

param: string, $spec

return: void

</function>

Sets the Solar_Uri::$query array from a string.

* Parameters:

 * string //$spec//: The query string to use; for example, "foor=bar&baz=dib".

* Returns void

Sets the Solar_Uri::$query array from a string.

This will overwrite any previous values.